original_title: Daniel Barenboim, Sir Georg Solti, András Schiff - Mozart concertos for 2 & 3 pianos
overview: Daniel Barenboim, Sir Georg Solti, András Schiff and the English Chamber Orchestra play Mozart's Piano Concerto No. 9 in E-flat major, K271 "Jeunehomme" (two pianos) and Piano Concerto No. 17 in G major, K453 (three pianos).
title: Daniel Barenboim, Sir Georg Solti, András Schiff - Mozart concertos for 2 & 3 pianos
